แซลมอนดองซีอิ๊วเป็นอาหาร
ที่สามารถเพิ่มค่าพลังงาน
และความอิ่มท้องของผู้เล่นได้ดี
ทำจากแซลมอนสด
ที่ผ่านการดองในซีอิ๊วสูตรพิเศษ
ซึ่งทำให้มีรสชาติหวานเค็มและมีกลิ่นหอม
สามารถพกพาและเก็บรักษาได้นาน
เหมาะสำหรับการเดินทาง
ในโลกที่เต็มไปด้วยอันตราย

ในช่วงก่อนเกิดการระบาดของซอมบี้ แซลมอนดองซีอิ๊วเป็นเมนูยอดนิยมในร้านอาหารญี่ปุ่นที่มีชื่อเสียงในเมืองซึ่งตอนนี้กลายเป็นซากปรักหักพัง นักท่องเที่ยวและชาวเมืองต่างต้องการลิ้มรสแซลมอนสดใหม่ที่ผ่านการดองในซีอิ๊วสูตรลับเฉพาะที่ทำให้รสชาติกลมกล่อมและมีความหวานเค็มพอดี การดองปลาไม่เพียงแต่ช่วยรักษาความสดของอาหาร แต่ยังเป็นวิธีการถนอมอาหารที่ทำให้สามารถเก็บรักษาได้นาน ซึ่งในโลกที่เต็มไปด้วยซอมบี้เช่นนี้ การมีแหล่งอาหารที่สามารถเก็บรักษาได้นานถือเป็นสิ่งสำคัญ วันหนึ่งคุณได้ค้นพบห้องครัวของร้านอาหารญี่ปุ่นเก่าแห่งนี้ ซึ่งยังมีส่วนผสมและบันทึกการทำแซลมอนดองซีอิ๊วอยู่ แม้ว่าจะไม่ได้สดเหมือนในอดีต แต่รสชาติและคุณค่าทางอาหารยังคงเดิม นี่เป็นโอกาสดีที่คุณจะได้ลิ้มรสอาหารที่เคยเป็นที่รักในอดีตและรับพลังงานในการต่อสู้เพื่อเอาชีวิตรอดต่อไป

"If you carry too many items in your backpack (inventory) you can become encumbered which lowers your movement speed. Items in your hotbar and worn clothing do not count.
Your inventory shows a number of unlocked and locked slots symbolic for how many items you can carry in your inventory without being encumbered. It is not necessary to place items on specific slots. Only the total amount of items in your backpack matters.

Food and drink items display a % value for the chance of getting Dysentery.
Levels of the Iron Gut perk reduce this chance.

Dysentery causes diarrhea which dehydrates you. This slows down the rate at which you regenerate stamina and health.
Goldenrod Tea and Pure Mineral Water will cure dysentery.
Rotten food can be eaten if you're starving but will hurt your health.

Many actions and events will cause a local increase on the Activity Map.

What affects the Activity Map:
- Flickering torches and to a lesser degree candles.
- Any workstation that burns fuel.
- Gunfire and explosions.
- Motor tools like chainsaws.
- Active traps like blade traps or shotgun turrets.
- Hitting or destroying metal or glass blocks or slamming metal doors.

If an area is 'hot' you will eventually have zombie scouts snooping around. If they spot you they will call in reinforcements.
Limit or stop these activities and this area will 'cool down' on it's own.
Lights or sounds are counted regardless of being noticeable to a player standing out in the open.
Electric generators or lights do not register.

Your current health is displayed in red and maximum health in grey. Damaged health or your maximum health cap is displayed in black.

Your current stamina is displayed in blue and maximum stamina is grey. Hunger lowers your maximum stamina cap and is displayed in black.

Your health and stamina recovery rate is determined by your hydration level.
Food and water bars are located below your belt slots / hotbar and the stats are found on the character page in the core and extended character stats tabs. Visible buffs will notify you if lack of food or water starts affecting you.

english: "Cooldowns give you the necessary breaks from ""bad"" actions in order to play the game while still allowing chat participation. Each ""bad"" spawn action fills up the cooldown bar. This will start a timed cooldown where viewers can still earn points and still use ""good"" actions. As your actionstage increases
"You can add custom interactions to the game by editing the twitch.xml file in your install folder. This includes actions
"There are two types of points used for actions
alle 10 Sekunden 1 Punkt (2 für Abonnenten). Diese Punkte sind nur im aktuellen Spielstand verfügbar. Sonderpunkte verdienst du

"All teammates that are in your party are eligible to be targeted by actions. Most buff/debuff actions will affect all party members by default. Party members can opt out of receiving actions/effects. When you opt out of vision effects
"The Pimp Pot is the reward for defeating you. All actions add a percentage of the cost to the Pimp Pot. When you are defeated

Using Progression unlocks more available actions for viewers based on your actionstage. These actions become more challenging as your actionstage increases. Viewers can type in #gs at any time to see your current actionstage. Progression mode is tailored towards a more traditional 7 Days to Die gameplay experience.

"Safe zones such as Trader and Land Claim areas offer protection from ""bad"" spawn actions. The status will change to ""Safe"" when you are inside the bounds of a safe zone. This should not be confused with the pause button that pauses all actions. "
"Votes allow viewers to choose structured special hordes or buffs/ debuffs multiple times per day. These are free for viewers to cast their choice. With Attack and Boss Votes

Default collection of Votes containing a wide variety of choices for viewers to help or hinder. This is a balanced risk vs. reward votes preset.

Armor increases your Armor Rating which is visible in the Character window. An armor rating of 90 reduces incoming damage by 90%. Armor also can provide some resistance to effects like bleeding or being stunned. Some armor slows you down and uses more stamina to move in.

Some cuts can be serious and cause you to bleed out. Carry bandages on your belt so you can quickly apply them with [action:local:Primary] to stop bleeding. Use [action:local:Secondary] on an ally to heal them.

"Cook bones into glue in a cooking pot or chemistry station. Glue is an essential ingredient to make duct tape
"Animal corpses and rotten remains can be harvested for hide
"To view an item's stats first select it in your inventory. The inspection window will show item stats

You can learn how to play the game by reading journal tips signified by the pen icon on the top tool bar.\nPress [action:local:Inventory][action:permanent:Journal] and click on the flashing pen icon to access journal entries.
"Magazines are the key to increasing your crafting skills. They can be found in mailboxes

On your HUD your health and stamina levels are shown as red and blue bars. Food and Water levels are shown as green and blue bars under your toolbelt. Open the Character window with [action:local:Inventory][action:permanent:Character] to see detailed player stats in the tabs below your character name.
"Investing points into a perk will increase the chances of finding related magazines
"Pickaxes are great for harvesting the various ores such as iron
"The stone axe works on everything but is slow. Iron tools are fast
The Right Tool for the job

In your inventory you can scrap many looted and harvested items down to their base material to save space.\nWhen scrapping items you lose 25% of the material but you can also smelt brass or iron items in a forge to get the full value.
Sledgehammers are great for breaking things but yield little or no harvest.
"If you crouch down you are sneaking. Enemies will have a harder time seeing and hearing you and you can increase your stealthiness with perks
Steel knuckles are the most devastating brawling weapon and can also be used to harvest meat from animals and remains.
The stone axe is a primitive starting tool used to gather resources using [action:local:Primary].\nUse [action:local:Secondary] to repair and upgrade blocks.
Are you a Twitch streamer? You can enable Twitch integration to allow your viewers to interact with your game. Look for the in-game Twitch Options button for more details.

Thank God it's almost closing time. I've had enough bullshit for one day.
"Trader Rekt is now open. I've got a hangover
"Trader Rekt is now open. We've got food and wares
Trader Rekt is open for business. Buy Rekt or get wrecked!
"We're having a 10% off sale right now
"All food and wares are 15% off for the next 5 minutes. I'll be back in 10
"I don't care who you killed to get this
"This is a nice piece. Don't know how you got it
"You did the job and you did it well. Thank you for that. Here's your reward. Now
"Welcome to Trader Rekt's. Let's get one thing straight. If you don't like something
"Welcome to Trader Rekt's. I don't guarantee a thing
Welcome to Trader Rekt's. Everything here has a full no money back guarantee.
Afternoon. Is it beer thirty yet?
"Afternoon. If you bring me a cold one
"If you want some fancy good afternoon greeting
"It's fuckin' hot out there this afternoon
"You're not scared of a blood moon
It's a bloody moon again. Time for a Bloody Mary.
You better buy some elixir and booze to get through the blood moon.
It's a blood moon. I'll bet my last duke you won't make it through the night.
"Good evening. I've had a few drinks
Happy hour ain't happy unless you bring me a beer.
It was a good evening until you came in. What do you want?
How's my favorite asshole doing tonight?
How did you get in here? Aren't we closed yet?
At least wipe that shit off your boots before you come into my shop.
Everything's for sale. Even to an idiot like you.
Make it snappy. I gotta take a crap.
Put away your weapon unless you'd like to die in my store.
"You're not bringing counterfeit money in here
You're welcome here if you shut the fuck up and buy something.
You better buy somethin' or you can get your smelly ass off my property.
You'd best keep clear of me.
It will be a good morning when you buy something and get the fuck out of here.
"Morning. If you try to say it's a good morning
Just fucking great. The last thing I see today is your ugly mug?
It fucking figures you're my last customer. This day can't get any worse.
"Listen you son of a bitch. If you ain't out the god damned door when I close
You gotta be the dumbest son of a bitch to get infected.
I don't think antibiotics can fix stupid.
I don't think there's any medicine that can fix dumbass.
All the best recipes take super corn. You might find some at Carl's Corn.
You can make your own Sham if you can find the recipe at one of the Shamways.
"That fucking asshole Carl was going to tell me his secret to making super corn and then he went missing. I think he might have some in his greenhouse
You can make your own beer with a chemistry station and a little know-how.
"I don't trust the water around here
"Here's a tip for you: don't cross me
Anyone that dies from infection is just plain lazy. You can make your own herbal antibiotics from basic ingredients and a campfire.
Are you about done stinking up my store? Hurry up and buy something.
Stop drooling all over the food!
Is that you tracking all the mud around my shop?
I was a farmer before the apocalypse. Damn good one too.
Why don't you make yourself useful and get me a beer.
"They say some pencil pushers at Higashi Labs started this mess. Come to think of it
"That fucking Trader Bob might be handy with a wrench
No loitering. Either buy something or get out.
Trader Hugh has got my respect. He shoots straight and supports the Duke. What's not to like?
Hurry it up! And stop eyeballing the tip jar!
"I don't know what kind of goody two shoes shit you've been pulling
"Some of those White River assholes were in here asking for you. Come to my store
"I guess you're some kind of hotshot because the Duke wants to meet you at his casino. Or maybe he'll just kill you like I would. Well
"Hey asshole! The Duke wants to see you for some god damned reason. Come to my store
"I'd say it's been an honor to work with you
What are you standing there for? Don't you have work to do?
Don't just stand there with your thumb up your ass. Get the job done.
"Can't say I'm not surprised. Good luck
"Let's get one thing straight: you're not working with me
Wipe that smirk off your face. Doing one job doesn't make us pals. Got it?
Great! Here you go. Don't spend it all in one place.
"Didn't we agree your first job was gonna be free? Damn
I knew you were a coward the moment I laid eyes on you.
You're turning me down? I oughta put a bullet in that thick skull of yours.
I've had enough of your bullshit. Get out of my sight.
Well you're either brave or stupid. Nobody turns me down around here.
I thought you might be yellow.
You must be half a zombie already. Or got shit for brains to cross me.
Are you out of yer god damned mind?
"Unbelievable. You drifters come in here looking for handouts
Nobody tells me no. Get this son of a bitch out of my sight.
You got some brass balls coming in here and turning me down.
Lazy ass son of a bitch.
Hey dipshit! I already gave you something to do.
You dumb son of a bitch! I already gave you some work.
Finish the fucking job I gave you and stop wasting my time.
You get your fuckin' ass out of here and get the job done!
I've got work if you don't mind getting your hands dirty.
"Let's make a pact. You do something for me
"If you want a job from me
I've got just the job for a simpleton like you.
I'm gonna make you an offer you can't refuse.
I got some shit work for a fuckup like you.
You can shove that right up yer ass.
You gotta be the dumbest son of a bitch I've ever seen. Can't you see we're overstocked on those?
"Are you trying to pull a fast one? The shelves are full
"I shot a low life one time
The Duke pays his bills and doesn't ask for credit or favors like those White River Clowns.
The Duke kills scumbags all the time. I'd watch my back if I were you.
Me and the Duke go way back. I used to gamble at his casino before the shit hit the fan.
"If you think the Duke is mean
That Noah fancies himself to be some kind of modern day Robin Hood. He's just a scumbag thief. You'd probably fit in good with him.
That White River outfit all ought to be hanged.
Noah's gotta be the dumbest son of a bitch thinking he can come in here and buy things on credit.
"If I see any White River scum
"Noah killed a few of the Duke's men
"I don't give a shit what people think about me
Who needs Trader Jen? I can cut my own god damned leg off just fine.
Trader Jen is all jugs and no brains.
"People can say what they want about me
"I don't give a damn if people like my food. When you're starving
Trader Joel is full of shit. I could whip his ass any day of the week.
The only thing good about The White River Settlers is watching the Duke hang 'em.
The Duke's just like me. He tells it like it is and everyone's scared of him.
"No refunds. Deals done. Now beat it
All that gawkin' at goods and that's all you buy?
Don't let the door hit you on your way out.
A sale is a sale. Even if it is to a scumbag like you.
You cheap-ass son of bitch! That's all you're gonna buy?
Get the hell out of my store! It's for real customers.
You cheap son of a bitch.
Just get the fuck out of here.
Some days I don't even know why I open the doors.
I'd go broke with more customers like you.
"I'd tell you to go fuck yourself
I knew you were a cheap mother fucker.
I knew you were a no-good thief the moment I laid eyes on you.
I put rat poison in that.
You no-good son of a bitch! Put that back!
If you do that again I'm gonna cut your god damned throat .
And people wonder why my prices are so high.
"I heard you've been greasin' up Bob's lug nuts. If you're ready for some real work
"I've got some real work for you
"Joel?! That son of a bitch will bend you over as soon as you turn around! Now get your ass in here
What the hell do you want this time?
"Take a look at the shit I got
Quit gawking. Either buy something or piss off!
Flash some cash or get lost.
Don’t test my patience. It's thinner than your wallet.
Make up your mind or make your way out.
Selling to even a dumbass like you.
Try anything smart and you'll get a new start.
You gonna buy some food or just stand there like a god damned idiot?
